# LF everywhere: the repo is edited from Fedora and Windows against one
# working tree, and tools on the NTFS mount intermittently rewrite files
# as CRLF. Normalising at the git boundary stops those flips reaching
# commits regardless of which side staged them.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary assets: never converted.
*.png binary
*.webp binary
*.bmp binary
*.ico binary
*.ttf binary
